<dl id="n11105l"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n11" href="#n11105l">N11 (VI.B.5)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n11all.htm#n11105l"> 105(l)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> spitting of righteous</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Then Hell, receiving Satan the prince, with sore reproach said unto him: O prince of perdition and chief of destruction, Beelzebub, the scorn of the angels and <mark>spitting of the righteous</mark>, why wouldest thou do this? <small> James, M. R, ed., <a name="APOC" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#APOC"><cite title="source">The Apocryphal New Testament</cite></a> (1924) 136</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
